        "subject": "LU-12506 mdc: Remove cdev_init",
        "message": "LU-12506 mdc: Remove cdev_init\n\nNOT FOR REAL USE.\n\nThis is a quick patch to enable mounting with more than 64\nMDTs while the actual bug is resolved.\n\nThis appears to mount & start safely and passes basic\ntesting, but attempts to use changelogs will likely crash\nclients.\n\nPutting minimal testing so as not to waste test resources.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I3e9bf66525e322e83cb4859ea3b34a9c13d469e4\n"
      },
